## рџљЂ Getting Started

### 1. Database Setup

```sql
CREATE DATABASE peta_sebaran CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci;
```

> If your MySQL root password is not empty, update [backend/.env](file:///D:/Peta-Sebaran/backend/.env) в†’ `DB_PASSWORD=yourpassword`

### 2. Backend

```bash
cd D:\Peta-Sebaran\backend

# Run migrations + seed demo data
php artisan migrate --seed

# Start dev server
php artisan serve        # в†’ http://localhost:8000
```

**Default credentials seeded:**
- `admin@dinsemarang.go.id` / `password`
- `staff@dinsemarang.go.id` / `password`

### 3. Frontend

```bash
cd D:\Peta-Sebaran\frontend
npm run dev              # в†’ http://localhost:5173
```

