## рџ—єпёЏ GDB в†’ GeoJSON Conversion

```bash
cd D:\Peta-Sebaran\gis-tools

# List layers in GDB
python convert_gdb_to_geojson.py --input "path/to/file.gdb" --list

# Convert a layer
python convert_gdb_to_geojson.py \
  --input  "path/to/file.gdb" \
  --output "./geojson" \
  --layer  "KiosRejomulyo"
```

Then upload the `.geojson` file via **Admin в†’ Layer GIS в†’ Upload GeoJSON (рџ“¤)**.

> Requires: `pip install gdal` OR `pip install geopandas fiona`

---

## рџ”‘ Key API Endpoints

```
POST  /api/auth/login              в†’ returns Sanctum token
GET   /api/dashboard/stats         в†’ public stats for charts
GET   /api/pasars                  в†’ market list
GET   /api/pasars/{id}/geojson     в†’ GeoJSON polygons for map

# Admin (Bearer token required)
GET/POST/PUT/DELETE  /api/admin/kios
POST                 /api/admin/layers/{id}/upload   в†ђ GeoJSON file
```

