## вњЁ Features Implemented

- [x] **Interactive Map** вЂ” Leaflet.js, custom emoji markers, GeoJSON polygon overlays, fly-to animation, kiosk detail popups
- [x] **Public Dashboard** вЂ” Chart.js doughnut (occupancy), bar (per-pasar), horizontal bar (categories), occupancy progress bars
- [x] **Admin CRUD** вЂ” Paginated kiosk table, search/filter, create/edit modal, delete with confirm
- [x] **GIS Layer Admin** вЂ” Create layer, toggle active, upload GeoJSON file, delete
- [x] **Sanctum Auth** вЂ” JWT-less token auth, Zustand persist store, protected routes
- [x] **Code Splitting** вЂ” `React.lazy()` + Vite `manualChunks` for Leaflet, Chart.js, admin bundle
- [x] **GDB Converter** вЂ” Python script with GDAL/geopandas, WGS84 reprojection, CLI
- [x] **Semarang Theme** вЂ” Blue `#0057A8` palette, Inter font, glassmorphism, hover animations
